Pre-Game Insights: Armenia took a hit when Latvia handed them a 2-0 defeat in their latest encounter.
The former did win the reverse match though, as they secured a triumph to their name by claiming a 2-1 win.
Armenia enter their upcoming game placed as number 97 in the FIFA world ranking.
There is a bit of a gap to opponents Latvia, who enter the game ranked number 137 in the world.
Armenia will attempt to get through the group stages effortlessly, thus dropping points here is not on the agenda.
